1. *Zadatak* za danas je da naučimo pet novih reči. (The *task* for today is to learn five new words.)
2. Kada sam završio *zadatak*, osetio sam olakšanje. (When I finished the *task*, I felt relieved.)
3. Nisam uspeo da rešim ovaj *zadatak* jer mi nedostaje informacija. (I couldn't solve this *task* because I lack information.)
4. Moramo da uradimo ovaj *zadatak* pre nego što odeš kući. (We need to complete this *task* before you go home.)
5. *Zadatak* je bio lako rešiti, ali sam se mučio sa drugim delom zadatka. (The *task* was easy to solve, but I struggled with the other part of the task.)
6. Profesor je dao težak *zadatak* za domaći. (The teacher gave a difficult *task* for homework.)
7. Molim te da mi pomogneš sa ovim *zadatkom*. (Please help me with this *task*.)
8. Da li ste razumeli šta je *zadatak* koji treba da obavimo? (Did you understand what is the *task* we need to do?)
9. Ukoliko ne budemo pažljivi, nećemo uspeti da završimo *zadatak* na vreme. (If we're not careful, we won't be able to finish the *task* on time.)
10. Zbog toga što nisam pažljivo pročitao *zadatak*, napravio sam grešku. (Because I didn't read the *task* carefully, I made a mistake.)